# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Bank of Agent — relay configuration
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Leave this UNSET (or empty) to run against the built-in, in-browser MOCK relay.
# The mock implements the full relay interface contract v0, so the entire demo
# loop (buy → call → transfer → redeem → call) works with zero backend.
#
# To go LIVE, set this to your real BoA relay base URL. That is the ONLY change
# required — no code edits. The app will hit `<URL>/v1/chat/completions`,
# `<URL>/boa/price`, etc. directly and disable the mock.
#
# NOTE: a real relay must send CORS headers and expose the metering header via
#       `Access-Control-Expose-Headers: x-boa-usage`.

# NEXT_PUBLIC_RELAY_URL=https://relay.boa.eth
